Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-ollama`, instrumenting the `ollama` Python SDK
(`chat`, `generate`, `embed`/`embeddings`, sync and async, streaming and
non-streaming) and emitting standard GenAI semantic conventions via
`opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires `OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
